<p class="ql-align-justify">疫情期间，许多富人开始在长岛汉普顿（Hamptons）置产，6个邮编地区累计收到6,500份迁往当地的住址变更申请，其中最高的是东汉普敦（East Hampton），收到2,769份，第二是南汉普敦（South Hampton），收到1,398份。有一些纽约人搬往更远的地区，有8,587份申请将邮件转寄至洛杉矶；超过1.3万份申请转往佛州的棕榈滩（Palm Beach）、布劳沃德（Broward）和迈阿密戴德（Miami-Dade）。</p>
➜移民快讯  魁北克启动直接雇主移民招聘门户网站
http://www.sohu.com/a/432392301_100269542	78300
<p>加拿大CIC消息</p>
<p>新的门户网站使雇主可以直接访问已经在魁北克或国外的潜在候选人，并从移民顾问提供的个性化支持中受益。</p>
<p>招聘门户网站的一项新功能使企业可以使用Arrima系统中的数据在魁北克省和国外招募移民求职者。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200509/0ce6ee4966b649099c2fa1c018a42e61.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>魁北克移民部部长纳丁·吉罗（Nadine Girault）于11月5日宣布了这一消息。</p>
<p>也是在这一天，魁北克移民部提供的雇主门户网站的新功能已为企业使用。</p>
<p>该新功能旨在方便选择最能满足该省当前劳动力市场需求的人员，新功能将使企业可以直接访问该部的网站，查阅移民候选人的概况，为他们提供工作并帮助启动移民程序。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200317/705808d33a044d43ae469ce05c4b239b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>原文</strong></p>
<h1><strong>Quebec launches direct employer-immigration recruitment portal</strong></h1>
<p>New portal allows employers to have direct access to potential candidates already in Québec or abroad and to benefit from personalized support offered by an immigration advisor.</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>A new feature of the Employer Portal allows businesses to recruit immigrant job seekers in Quebec and abroad using data from the Arrima system.</p>
<p>Quebec’s Minister of Immigration, Francization and Integration, Nadine Girault, made the announcement on November 5.</p>
<p>It was also on that date that the new functionality of the Employer Portal, a service offered by the Quebec Ministry of Immigration, was made available to businesses.</p>
<p>Designed to facilitate the selection of the people who best meet current labour market needs in the province, the new feature will allow businesses to go directly to the ministry’s website, consult the profiles of immigration candidates, offer them a job and help initiate the immigration process.</p>